<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,356,546,573]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Bathyceramaster</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Mah, C. L." box="[364,503,546,573]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31" pagination="101 - 141" refId="ref47633" refString="Mah, C. L. (2016 a) Deep-sea (&gt; 1000 m) Goniasteridae (Valvatida; Asteroidea) from the North Pacific, including an overview of Sibogaster, Bathyceramaster n. gen. and three new species. Zootaxa, 4175 (2), 101 - 141. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4175.2.1" type="journal article" year="2016">Mah 2016a</bibRefCitation>
